hopobject.body: I'd like some euros tiro segno nazionale bologna Anyone up for a game of tennis? Count us in if it's with these hotties! As the U.S. Open 2013 comes to an end, we celebrate the best-looking players on the tennis court, both past and present ... Serena Williams charged the net against Victoria Azarenka of Belarus to snag her 17th Grand Slam singles title, winning the 2013 U.S. Open on Sept. 8, 2013. Then again, she always keeps us on our toes ...
